WEBVTT

00:11.150 --> 00:16.690
[Flower-Crowned General's Mansion]

00:15.720 --> 00:16.560
Whoa!

00:25.230 --> 00:27.490
My Lord, we're at the General's Mansion.

00:27.820 --> 00:28.480
Changyu.

00:28.500 --> 00:29.140
What are you doing?

00:29.140 --> 00:29.890
I miss you.

00:30.500 --> 00:33.690
[Flower-Crowned General's Mansion]

00:31.000 --> 00:31.640
Changyu.

00:31.660 --> 00:32.720
Don't be like this.

00:33.020 --> 00:34.150
Calm down.

00:40.350 --> 00:42.200
His Lordship is seriously injured.

00:42.200 --> 00:43.600
Here is the plan.
You guys stay here and keep watch.

00:43.600 --> 00:44.990
I'll go find a doctor.

00:46.670 --> 00:48.350
A doctor won't help with this.

00:49.560 --> 00:50.430
Why not?

00:58.350 --> 00:59.530
Why won't a doctor help?

00:59.530 --> 01:00.790
You don't understand?

01:05.280 --> 01:05.920
I see.

01:06.760 --> 01:08.280
I'll go to the Imperial Hospital
to find a royal physician.

01:08.280 --> 01:09.440
No need for that.

01:09.470 --> 01:10.430
Inside there...

01:11.400 --> 01:12.800
I can't explain it to you.

01:13.760 --> 01:14.480
You guys,

01:14.640 --> 01:16.200
find a few sensible older maids

01:16.200 --> 01:17.120
and have them stand at the four corners

01:17.120 --> 01:17.760
and keep watch from a distance.

01:17.760 --> 01:18.870
Don't let anyone get close.

01:18.870 --> 01:19.700
-Yes.
-Yes, Brother.

01:19.700 --> 01:20.220
Go.

01:21.350 --> 01:22.150
What about me?

01:22.280 --> 01:24.000
Just don't make trouble. Come with me.

01:24.000 --> 01:24.870
But...

01:25.480 --> 01:26.510
I've realized something about you.

01:26.510 --> 01:27.789
You can't just fight wars all the time.

01:27.789 --> 01:29.650
You need to understand life a bit.

01:30.150 --> 01:31.039
Which aspect?

01:54.509 --> 01:58.110
♪ In a lifetime of storms,
a fleeting bloom ♪

01:55.360 --> 01:56.900
Calm down first.

01:57.880 --> 01:58.960
I'll get a doctor.

01:58.539 --> 02:01.280
♪ The most beautiful scenery
becomes a poem ♪

02:01.810 --> 02:05.190
♪ For a chance encounter ♪

02:06.210 --> 02:09.710
♪ A single letter of longing,
half a lifetime apart ♪

02:10.340 --> 02:12.410
♪ I'll burn out my passion for you ♪

02:12.940 --> 02:16.480
♪ Just for a glance ♪

02:16.840 --> 02:17.600
♪ In this life ♪

02:17.620 --> 02:20.310
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

02:20.329 --> 02:21.940
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

02:22.270 --> 02:23.120
♪ On this journey ♪

02:23.150 --> 02:26.130
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

02:26.150 --> 02:28.130
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

02:28.150 --> 02:29.000
♪ After we part ♪

02:29.020 --> 02:31.860
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

02:31.880 --> 02:34.070
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

02:32.870 --> 02:33.920
Who am I?

02:34.090 --> 02:38.820
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

02:39.280 --> 02:40.240
♪ In this life ♪

02:40.260 --> 02:43.079
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

02:43.110 --> 02:44.860
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

02:43.800 --> 02:44.910
Fan Changyu.

02:44.910 --> 02:45.770
♪ On this journey ♪

02:45.800 --> 02:48.640
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

02:48.670 --> 02:50.770
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

02:50.820 --> 02:51.640
♪ After we part ♪

02:51.660 --> 02:54.579
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

02:54.600 --> 02:56.720
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

02:56.920 --> 03:01.970
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

03:02.010 --> 03:07.150
♪ We'll never be apart ♪

03:20.040 --> 03:22.500
It seems there is no need for me
to intervene.

03:22.680 --> 03:23.630
This is even better.

03:23.630 --> 03:25.030
Nature takes its course.

03:25.150 --> 03:26.150
Royal Physician,

03:26.190 --> 03:27.990
you haven't even checked on him.

03:28.520 --> 03:30.150
Are you the royal physician,

03:30.400 --> 03:31.870
or am I?

03:32.520 --> 03:33.100
I...

03:34.140 --> 03:36.630
I told you that you don't need a doctor
for such things.

03:36.630 --> 03:38.360
And you actually invited
a royal physician?

03:38.360 --> 03:39.490
It was a wasted trip.

03:39.829 --> 03:40.890
Let's go, let's go.

03:42.680 --> 03:43.560
You two.

03:44.470 --> 03:45.030
Let's go.

03:49.280 --> 03:51.000
So what exactly is life?

05:25.020 --> 05:30.280
[Pursuit of Jade]

05:30.400 --> 05:33.030
[Episode 38]

05:41.430 --> 05:43.390
The Emperor got a slap in the face?

05:45.600 --> 05:48.290
It was worth the fire I sent him.

05:55.390 --> 05:56.390
It's just a pity

05:56.630 --> 05:59.480
that the Marquis of Wu'an
and Fan Changyu escaped.

06:00.390 --> 06:02.390
Your Li family has a traitor within.

06:03.310 --> 06:05.310
Shouldn't he be punished properly?

06:05.560 --> 06:07.000
My grandson

06:07.430 --> 06:11.030
was bewitched by the Marquis of Wu'an
and Fan Changyu for a moment

06:11.120 --> 06:12.850
and ruined today's grand plan.

06:14.160 --> 06:15.750
I will bear all the blame

06:17.680 --> 06:19.190
for him.

06:19.750 --> 06:21.830
Grand Tutor,
there's no need for such seriousness.

06:21.830 --> 06:23.120
In this way,

06:24.720 --> 06:26.310
we have effectively cut off
any possibility

06:26.310 --> 06:29.160
of cooperation between
the Marquis of Wu'an and Qi Sheng.

06:29.160 --> 06:30.160
Besides,

06:30.630 --> 06:32.270
I even prepared a big gift

06:32.290 --> 06:33.780
for that butcher girl.

06:33.920 --> 06:35.560
If Wei Yan knows it,

06:36.240 --> 06:38.270
he will be very happy.

06:38.950 --> 06:40.270
What is it?

06:42.690 --> 06:45.390
The Tiger Tally he has been longing for.

06:46.820 --> 06:48.430
The Tiger Tally

06:49.070 --> 06:51.930
used to mobilize troops
in the Northwest back then?

06:52.950 --> 06:54.560
This is just the appetizer.

06:55.040 --> 06:56.950
The main course is yet to come.

06:59.430 --> 07:00.070
Please.

07:00.330 --> 07:00.970
Alright.

07:02.120 --> 07:02.750
Please.

07:51.450 --> 07:52.210
Mother.

07:52.750 --> 07:55.080
Look, I picked so many osmanthus flowers.

07:55.730 --> 07:57.400
Good job, Zheng.

07:57.470 --> 07:58.830
Later,

07:58.830 --> 08:00.870
let's use these
to make osmanthus candy. Okay?

08:00.870 --> 08:02.190
Yay!

08:04.120 --> 08:04.780
Smell them.

08:31.400 --> 08:32.159
Mother!

08:36.669 --> 08:37.840
You're here, Zheng?

08:37.870 --> 08:39.870
Sit down. Have some osmanthus cake.

08:59.910 --> 09:00.870
I finally

09:03.310 --> 09:04.680
get to see you again.

09:12.020 --> 09:13.790
Now that you have someone by your side

09:13.790 --> 09:16.050
who understands and cherishes you,

09:16.270 --> 09:17.720
I can rest easy.

09:22.670 --> 09:23.720
Remember…

09:23.960 --> 09:25.510
osmanthus cake

09:26.320 --> 09:27.960
is my favorite.

09:42.200 --> 09:43.080
What's wrong?

09:43.600 --> 09:45.000
Did you have a nightmare?

09:45.550 --> 09:46.320
I'm fine.

09:47.390 --> 09:49.450
I just had a dream about my childhood.

10:07.240 --> 10:08.000
Changyu.

10:09.710 --> 10:11.490
For you to be with me like this…

10:12.600 --> 10:14.480
I've treated you unfairly.

10:15.670 --> 10:17.080
When I settle down,

10:17.780 --> 10:20.150
I will definitely give you
a proper wedding.

10:20.150 --> 10:21.810
You didn't treat me unfairly.

10:23.200 --> 10:24.930
I am willing to marry Xie Zheng.

10:25.150 --> 10:27.650
But Yan Zheng married into my family.

10:28.440 --> 10:30.530
That was also a wonderful wedding.

10:32.750 --> 10:35.280
We haven't signed
the Divorce Agreement yet.

10:37.080 --> 10:38.270
Don't you deny it.

10:41.440 --> 10:42.240
I won't.

10:43.790 --> 10:45.650
I will be your matrilocal husband

10:45.860 --> 10:46.980
for life.

10:54.540 --> 10:55.870
This trip to the Capital

10:56.910 --> 10:59.690
has been one trouble after another.

11:00.150 --> 11:01.440
Now I just want to clear Father's name

11:01.440 --> 11:02.670
as soon as possible,

11:03.150 --> 11:04.510
return to Lin'an,

11:05.360 --> 11:07.120
and live a peaceful life.

11:09.390 --> 11:10.850
But regarding last night,

11:10.870 --> 11:12.730
I'm afraid it wasn't that simple.

11:15.120 --> 11:16.000
Don't worry.

11:16.750 --> 11:18.000
I have a plan.

11:22.630 --> 11:24.020
[Where Compassion and Grace Meet]

11:47.870 --> 11:48.910
Be... be careful.

11:49.000 --> 11:49.550
Easy.

11:54.140 --> 11:57.160
I thought I'd never see you again.

11:57.480 --> 12:00.240
I thought I was going to die there.

12:00.260 --> 12:01.560
It's alright now.

12:01.630 --> 12:03.350
I'm right here with you.

12:05.910 --> 12:06.840
Don't cry.

12:09.480 --> 12:10.320
It's alright.

12:22.250 --> 12:23.510
Last night,

12:25.480 --> 12:28.010
did you stay here
and take care of me all night?

12:29.070 --> 12:29.700
Yes.

12:30.600 --> 12:32.270
You haven't rested at all?

12:33.390 --> 12:34.550
Then how could you...

12:34.550 --> 12:36.030
Yesterday, to save me,

12:36.030 --> 12:38.030
you rushed into the fire.

12:38.200 --> 12:40.240
I was so afraid you'd die in there.

12:40.270 --> 12:41.630
-Alright, alright.
-You must be hurt.

12:41.630 --> 12:43.430
-Let me see.
-Alright, alright.

12:43.510 --> 12:44.720
You're very weak right now.

12:44.720 --> 12:45.750
Stop talking.

12:47.360 --> 12:48.240
Listen to me.

12:53.480 --> 12:54.390
In the past,

12:56.150 --> 12:57.720
I was always so timid.

12:59.440 --> 13:00.560
But this time,

13:01.000 --> 13:02.080
I want to tell you,

13:02.550 --> 13:03.320
from now on,

13:04.750 --> 13:05.930
no matter what happens,

13:05.930 --> 13:07.510
I will stay by your side.

13:07.670 --> 13:10.120
And only I can take care of you.

13:37.480 --> 13:39.120
This Tiger Tally doesn't match.

13:39.120 --> 13:39.910
It's fake.

13:41.750 --> 13:42.610
Your Highness,

13:42.960 --> 13:44.360
this Tiger Tally is real.

13:44.840 --> 13:47.600
Crown Prince Chengde and General Xie
can't hold on much longer.

13:47.600 --> 13:49.000
Jinzhou is in danger!

13:49.150 --> 13:52.120
For the sake of the country
and the people,

13:52.200 --> 13:54.860
please send troops
to rescue them immediately!

14:16.840 --> 14:17.670
General.

14:19.510 --> 14:20.150
Come in.

14:24.150 --> 14:24.910
What is it?

14:25.150 --> 14:25.870
General,

14:26.030 --> 14:28.390
Guard Jin has been waiting outside
for a long time.

14:28.390 --> 14:30.920
He asked that you see him
as soon as you wake up.

14:31.270 --> 14:32.000
I see.

14:32.390 --> 14:33.030
You may go.

14:37.200 --> 14:38.200
There is a letter here.

14:38.200 --> 14:39.600
It's for you personally.

14:47.600 --> 14:49.630
[To Fan Changyu]

14:55.570 --> 15:00.040
[I'm fine now. Don't worry about me.
Qianqian]

15:00.140 --> 15:01.450
It's from Qianqian?

15:09.240 --> 15:10.170
The Tiger Tally?

15:11.120 --> 15:12.520
Where did this come from?

15:12.630 --> 15:13.430
Last night,

15:13.600 --> 15:15.320
a maid delivering a letter was found dead

15:15.320 --> 15:17.380
at the gate of our General's Mansion.

15:19.270 --> 15:20.510
Help!

15:20.910 --> 15:24.690
[Flower-Crowned General's Mansion]

15:25.720 --> 15:27.070
Help!

15:33.080 --> 15:34.510
Help!

15:37.150 --> 15:37.790
Guards!

15:38.740 --> 15:41.040
[Flower-Crowned General's Mansion]

15:49.120 --> 15:49.960
She's dead?

15:53.170 --> 15:54.830
You guys, bring your weapons.

15:54.860 --> 15:56.630
Search around
for any suspicious individuals.

15:55.600 --> 15:58.670
[Flower-Crowned General's Mansion]

15:56.750 --> 15:57.320
Yes!

16:03.150 --> 16:04.410
That dream just now...

16:05.270 --> 16:06.510
Could it be that

16:06.870 --> 16:09.530
Heaven also wants to seek justice
for my father?

16:10.440 --> 16:11.080
General.

16:11.320 --> 16:13.080
Someone named Lady Shisan
wants to see you.

16:13.080 --> 16:14.150
Lady Shisan?

16:16.230 --> 16:17.160
I'll go with you.

16:17.480 --> 16:18.240
No need.

16:19.120 --> 16:20.580
I want to talk to her alone.

16:35.270 --> 16:37.120
That lowly maid
has already delivered the Tiger Tally

16:37.120 --> 16:38.590
to Fan Changyu.

16:44.150 --> 16:45.100
Deal with it.

16:45.320 --> 16:45.920
Yes.

17:01.440 --> 17:02.970
You weren't drunk that day?

17:09.069 --> 17:10.440
I love you so much.

17:10.589 --> 17:12.150
Why did you do this to me?

17:13.510 --> 17:14.680
Every time I think

17:16.069 --> 17:17.310
you won't leave me

17:17.829 --> 17:19.890
and that you're willing to be with me,

17:20.030 --> 17:22.099
it always ends up like this.

17:22.270 --> 17:23.790
Is my love so cheap

17:24.240 --> 17:25.790
that you can just trample on it?

17:25.790 --> 17:27.000
That isn't love.

17:27.109 --> 17:27.790
It's possessiveness!

17:27.790 --> 17:29.250
It's a desire for control!

17:32.110 --> 17:33.910
I am about to become the Emperor.

17:33.960 --> 17:34.920
Without me,

17:35.480 --> 17:36.810
you won't be an empress.

17:37.720 --> 17:39.130
You are nothing.

17:39.310 --> 17:41.490
I don't care about being an empress.

17:41.680 --> 17:42.610
Without you,

17:43.880 --> 17:45.280
I will live a better life.

17:54.000 --> 17:55.980
Kill me if you have the guts.

18:11.750 --> 18:13.610
Are you alright? Are you alright?

18:16.270 --> 18:17.730
I... I'm begging you.

18:18.310 --> 18:19.510
Please tell me—

18:19.590 --> 18:21.520
as long as you don't leave me,

18:22.070 --> 18:23.270
whatever you want,

18:23.640 --> 18:24.770
I will give it to you!

18:26.200 --> 18:27.910
I don't want anything.

18:30.240 --> 18:32.220
I just want to leave you forever.

18:51.110 --> 18:52.530
You forced me to do this.

18:52.880 --> 18:54.160
Bring the shackles!

18:54.310 --> 18:54.980
Yes.

19:07.160 --> 19:08.830
These are cast from refined steel.

19:08.830 --> 19:10.590
Even blades and axes cannot break them.

19:10.590 --> 19:11.880
If you want to escape,

19:12.110 --> 19:14.640
you must cut off one of our hands.

19:15.680 --> 19:16.880
You're crazy.

19:17.720 --> 19:19.320
You must have lost your mind!

19:20.920 --> 19:22.080
You can't escape.

19:23.480 --> 19:24.630
In this lifetime,

19:25.160 --> 19:26.680
you belong only to me.

19:47.000 --> 19:49.000
I didn't expect you to be alive.

19:53.590 --> 19:54.920
Why do you want to see me?

19:55.340 --> 19:56.720
To avenge Sui Yuanqing?

19:59.030 --> 20:00.310
It seems that

20:00.790 --> 20:03.850
I'm the only one left who still remembers
to avenge him.

20:08.440 --> 20:09.440
This is for you.

20:10.240 --> 20:11.700
Sui Yuanqing gave it to me.

20:12.270 --> 20:13.110
And this.

20:18.030 --> 20:19.680
I'm leaving you a way out.

20:19.790 --> 20:22.350
Take this and go find Fan Changyu,

20:22.350 --> 20:24.070
and I will give you a...

20:24.240 --> 20:25.830
token of loyalty.

20:29.480 --> 20:30.880
The Tiger Tally is yours.

20:31.400 --> 20:32.550
And he is dead.

20:33.920 --> 20:34.930
I guess

20:35.510 --> 20:37.280
he just wanted Qi Min

20:37.440 --> 20:39.300
to be doomed eternally.

20:39.400 --> 20:40.260
What about you?

20:43.690 --> 20:44.730
What do you want?

20:47.750 --> 20:48.510
Me?

20:50.480 --> 20:52.020
I used to think

20:53.240 --> 20:55.100
you and Xie Zheng were my enemies.

20:55.750 --> 20:57.070
You killed my brothers.

20:57.070 --> 20:59.680
And Xie Zheng wiped out
my Qingfeng Stronghold.

20:59.680 --> 21:01.070
Later, I felt that

21:02.440 --> 21:03.970
he played with my feelings,

21:04.270 --> 21:05.110
causing me and Qingfeng Stronghold

21:05.110 --> 21:06.830
to fall into ruin.

21:07.830 --> 21:09.640
But today I realized,

21:11.440 --> 21:14.170
worldly grievances
are born of cause and effect.

21:15.110 --> 21:16.510
Revenge is endless.

21:17.270 --> 21:18.630
And all this killing

21:19.240 --> 21:20.440
is never-ending too.

21:22.350 --> 21:23.640
I've given you the Tiger Tally.

21:23.640 --> 21:24.200
It...

21:24.480 --> 21:25.790
Take the head with you.

21:27.030 --> 21:28.360
I don't need it anymore.

21:29.110 --> 21:30.770
You can leave his body intact.

21:45.480 --> 21:46.790
Thank you for today.

21:50.150 --> 21:52.680
I'll have someone get you
a new travel permit.

21:52.790 --> 21:54.250
You'll be free from now on.

21:55.400 --> 21:56.660
Consider it repayment

21:57.440 --> 21:59.240
for your kindness to Changning.

22:01.010 --> 22:02.740
But as for the score between us,

22:03.960 --> 22:05.620
we'll settle it when I return.

22:10.180 --> 22:12.130
I hope the next time we meet,

22:12.590 --> 22:13.720
you're still alive.

22:24.110 --> 22:25.730
[Talisman of Army]

22:30.720 --> 22:32.240
Qianqian sent this.

22:33.310 --> 22:35.040
I dreamed of Father last night.

22:35.070 --> 22:36.870
I woke up to see this Tiger Tally.

22:37.720 --> 22:39.180
But I don't understand why

22:40.790 --> 22:43.030
Lord Changxin framed my father.

22:43.590 --> 22:45.390
Why should the defeat at Jinzhou

22:46.680 --> 22:49.540
and the deaths
of hundreds of thousands of soldiers

22:50.830 --> 22:53.030
all be blamed on my father?

22:55.030 --> 22:58.230
My parents had been living in anonymity
for over a decade.

22:59.310 --> 23:00.160
Why...

23:01.880 --> 23:03.410
why were they still killed?

23:10.640 --> 23:13.370
I want to clear my father's name
before the world.

23:15.680 --> 23:16.590
Your father

23:17.720 --> 23:20.120
and the soldiers of Jinzhou
who died in vain

23:20.440 --> 23:21.840
all deserve justice.

23:22.830 --> 23:24.160
But right now,

23:25.000 --> 23:26.800
this pair of Tiger Tallies alone

23:27.830 --> 23:29.030
is not enough to prove

23:29.110 --> 23:31.200
that Wei Yan was the mastermind.

23:32.850 --> 23:34.910
The mad palace maid who knew the truth

23:35.090 --> 23:36.890
has already died in the fire.

23:37.510 --> 23:39.840
There's nothing left in Qingyuan Palace.

23:41.440 --> 23:43.810
Everyone involved in this matter

23:45.350 --> 23:47.070
has been silenced by Wei Yan.

23:47.680 --> 23:50.540
The mad maid's former mistress
was Consort Virtue.

23:51.510 --> 23:54.910
What is the relationship between
Consort Virtue and Wei Yan?

23:55.750 --> 23:58.550
It's rumored in the palace
that they had an affair.

23:58.960 --> 24:01.070
Then what exactly happened back then?

24:01.070 --> 24:02.730
Are there no clues left at all?

24:04.450 --> 24:05.410
That Qi Sheng...

24:05.830 --> 24:07.310
Could he know something?

24:08.920 --> 24:10.160
Don't be anxious.

24:12.270 --> 24:13.940
Even if Qi Sheng knows something,

24:13.940 --> 24:15.400
he wouldn't dare to say it.

24:16.170 --> 24:18.010
He has been a puppet for decades.

24:18.830 --> 24:21.130
He is terrified of Wei Yan.

24:21.330 --> 24:23.730
He certainly wouldn't dare to pursue this.

24:24.790 --> 24:25.960
Now,

24:27.440 --> 24:29.000
if we want to take down Wei Yan

24:29.000 --> 24:30.200
and make him confess,

24:32.240 --> 24:33.440
we can only use force.

24:35.440 --> 24:37.440
I called him Uncle for over 20 years.

24:37.880 --> 24:39.640
I know his nature all too well.

24:41.510 --> 24:42.200
I'm afraid

24:43.960 --> 24:45.960
he has already started a rebellion.

24:50.310 --> 24:51.350
Don't worry.

24:52.540 --> 24:55.140
I will gather
all the main forces of the Xie Army

24:55.680 --> 24:56.800
to seek justice

24:57.680 --> 24:59.240
for your father and mine.

25:16.440 --> 25:19.480
So it has come to this, after all.

25:24.250 --> 25:25.580
In that case,

25:26.640 --> 25:28.830
we will act ahead of schedule.

25:30.000 --> 25:31.200
Pass my order.

25:31.750 --> 25:34.350
Deploy the troops
back to the Capital immediately.

25:34.350 --> 25:35.030
Yes!

25:37.150 --> 25:37.950
At my command!

25:38.510 --> 25:40.110
Spread the news that Fan Changyu

25:40.110 --> 25:42.370
is the daughter of the traitor Wei Qilin!

25:42.550 --> 25:43.680
As soon as possible!

25:43.790 --> 25:44.440
Yes!

26:05.240 --> 26:09.700
[Graceful and Ethereal]

26:28.870 --> 26:30.160
Flower-Crowned General.

26:30.160 --> 26:31.680
by regulation, anyone who wants
to beat the Petition Drum

26:31.680 --> 26:33.640
without authorization
must first be paraded through the streets

26:33.640 --> 26:35.400
and subjected to public censure,

26:35.400 --> 26:38.860
only then may they strike the drum
to present their grievance.

26:42.450 --> 26:44.940
[In Memory of Wan, My Late Mother,
Xie Linshan's Wife]

26:44.940 --> 26:45.940
[In Memory of My Late Father, Xie Linshan]

26:45.960 --> 26:49.480
[Guo's Wine House]

26:54.830 --> 26:55.680
It's her!

26:55.720 --> 26:57.030
Everyone, come and look!

26:57.030 --> 26:57.840
It's her!

26:57.920 --> 26:59.880
She is the daughter of the big traitor!

26:59.880 --> 27:01.550
None of you in the Wei family
are any good!

27:01.550 --> 27:03.000
My father died in battle in Jinzhou!

27:03.000 --> 27:03.750
Make her pay with her life!

27:03.750 --> 27:04.640
What nonsense are you talking about?

27:04.640 --> 27:05.310
You are spouting filth!

27:05.310 --> 27:06.750
What nonsense are you talking about?
Do you have proof?

27:06.750 --> 27:07.400
Don't talk nonsense!

27:07.400 --> 27:08.720
My sister is innocent!

27:08.610 --> 27:10.350
[In Memory of Wan, My Late Mother,
Xie Linshan's Wife]

27:09.640 --> 27:10.510
Father.

27:10.350 --> 27:12.350
[In Memory of My Late Father, Xie Linshan]

27:11.310 --> 27:12.160
Mother.

27:13.310 --> 27:14.910
I've been an unfilial child.

27:15.960 --> 27:17.560
I pray your spirits in Heaven

27:18.920 --> 27:20.000
will forgive me.

27:27.310 --> 27:28.070
Beat her!

27:28.070 --> 27:29.070
Beat her to death!

27:29.590 --> 27:32.920
If you keep spouting nonsense,
I'll tear your mouths apart!

27:34.590 --> 27:36.640
The big traitor,

27:36.750 --> 27:38.970
Wei Qilin.

27:39.030 --> 27:41.180
He escorted the grain

27:41.350 --> 27:43.180
with no loyalty

27:43.530 --> 27:47.620
and cost 100,000 heroes their lives!

27:48.550 --> 27:50.350
Hit her!

27:54.070 --> 27:54.990
Hit her!

27:55.020 --> 27:56.020
Hit her!

28:01.110 --> 28:02.510
Kill her!

28:02.510 --> 28:03.160
Hit her!

28:05.350 --> 28:06.560
Beat her!

28:06.720 --> 28:08.200
Beat her to death!

28:10.640 --> 28:11.270
Sister!

28:11.310 --> 28:12.030
Fan!

28:13.120 --> 28:15.180
How can someone like her be a general?

28:15.430 --> 28:16.520
Who threw it?

28:16.590 --> 28:17.640
-Who threw it?
-Who threw it?

28:17.640 --> 28:18.640
-Good job!
-Well done!

28:18.640 --> 28:19.280
Good job!

28:19.310 --> 28:20.620
-Will you ever stop?
-You want to get physical?

28:20.620 --> 28:21.510
Stop!

28:26.850 --> 28:28.280
My father is Wei Qilin.

28:29.220 --> 28:30.580
But he is not a traitor.

28:31.090 --> 28:32.490
He was wrongly accused.

28:32.590 --> 28:33.940
-That's your father!
-Your father caused their death!

28:33.940 --> 28:35.350
Of course you'd say he's innocent!

28:35.350 --> 28:36.030
Exactly!

28:36.080 --> 28:36.870
Hit her!

28:36.920 --> 28:37.940
Enough is enough!

28:38.270 --> 28:39.160
Back off! All of you, back off!

28:39.160 --> 28:40.220
Kill her!

28:41.000 --> 28:42.270
Officials are handling the case!

28:42.270 --> 28:43.760
Bystanders, stand back!

28:44.510 --> 28:45.090
Back off!

28:45.110 --> 28:45.910
Step back!

28:45.940 --> 28:46.720
Move back!

28:47.110 --> 28:47.880
Are you alright?

28:47.880 --> 28:48.820
Nonsense!

28:49.070 --> 28:50.310
Flower-Crowned General?

28:50.310 --> 28:51.840
More like Traitor General!

28:51.850 --> 28:52.640
Shut up!

28:53.510 --> 28:55.640
Did any of you see it with your own eyes?

28:55.750 --> 28:57.720
Are you sure what you heard and saw

28:58.110 --> 28:59.590
is the truth?

29:13.010 --> 29:13.940
I'll go with you.

29:15.110 --> 29:16.440
We'll go with you too.

29:43.790 --> 29:44.850
The rest of the way,

29:45.880 --> 29:46.960
I'll walk alone.

29:51.280 --> 29:52.610
Once you take this step,

29:54.390 --> 29:55.870
there's no turning back.

29:58.750 --> 29:59.800
Let me go.

30:05.770 --> 30:06.640
Let her go.

30:24.830 --> 30:26.560
I'm Fan Changyu from Xigu Lane,

30:26.830 --> 30:28.720
Lin'an Town, Qingping County.

30:29.640 --> 30:30.410
I have come

30:31.440 --> 30:32.970
to file an imperial appeal.

30:33.170 --> 30:34.230
Those who file an imperial appeal,

30:34.230 --> 30:35.290
if the accusations are false,

30:35.290 --> 30:36.450
commit the crime
of deceiving the Sovereign.

30:36.450 --> 30:38.110
The penalty is immediate beheading.

30:38.110 --> 30:39.840
Have you thought this through?

30:40.350 --> 30:41.440
I have.

30:43.000 --> 30:44.330
This trip is,

30:44.360 --> 30:46.570
first, to denounce
the injustice of Heaven.

30:44.460 --> 30:49.180
[Yin]

30:48.020 --> 30:49.270
Wei Qilin,

30:49.270 --> 30:51.720
you are a traitor, worse than a beast!

30:49.350 --> 30:51.370
[Wei Qilin, Traitor of Great Yin]

30:51.340 --> 30:55.280
♪ The world is vast ♪

30:51.720 --> 30:53.270
-Traitor
-Traitor Wei!

30:53.270 --> 30:54.200
Traitor Wei!

30:53.570 --> 30:55.010
[Wei Qilin]

30:54.200 --> 30:54.750
Beat him!

30:55.680 --> 30:58.360
Second,
to accuse the Emperor of ignorance!

30:56.730 --> 31:02.720
♪ The storm is rising ♪

30:57.740 --> 31:02.660
[Think with Caution]

31:00.240 --> 31:01.550
Who's beating the drum?

31:01.550 --> 31:02.880
Who's beating the drum?

31:02.880 --> 31:03.680
Your Majesty.

31:03.830 --> 31:06.140
It's the Flower-Crowned General
beating the Petition Drum.

31:04.310 --> 31:08.610
♪ Day and night ♪

31:06.200 --> 31:08.730
She says she wants
to file an imperial appeal.

31:10.130 --> 31:13.460
♪ We strive to save the world ♪

31:10.280 --> 31:11.550
Didn't Grand Tutor Li say

31:11.550 --> 31:13.880
we could use Xie Zheng and Fan Changyu
to deal with Wei Yan?

31:13.880 --> 31:15.050
Deal with him, my ass!

31:15.050 --> 31:16.910
She is beating the Petition Drum!

31:17.490 --> 31:21.700
♪ All people ♪

31:19.960 --> 31:20.850
And third,

31:22.290 --> 31:24.280
to indict
the treacherous ministers in power!

31:22.900 --> 31:28.310
♪ Are part of the past ♪

31:27.190 --> 31:28.380
I, Fan Changyu,

31:29.000 --> 31:31.360
am here today to clear my father's name!

31:30.540 --> 31:35.320
♪ What's the date today? ♪

31:35.850 --> 31:42.690
♪ How lamentable ♪

31:53.170 --> 31:56.150
♪ What's the date today? ♪

31:56.850 --> 32:00.480
♪ How lamentable ♪

32:09.200 --> 32:10.110
Zheng,

32:11.480 --> 32:13.880
I made these osmanthus cakes myself.

32:14.640 --> 32:15.750
Remember,

32:18.480 --> 32:20.200
what I love most

32:20.200 --> 32:21.750
is this osmanthus cake.

32:48.440 --> 32:51.080
Yan, when you read this,
it's like seeing me.

32:51.590 --> 32:53.520
When you return in triumph and read this,

32:53.520 --> 32:55.900
I will likely have passed away.

32:55.960 --> 32:57.750
I only wish that in the next life,

32:57.750 --> 32:59.220
you will be a commoner,

32:59.310 --> 33:01.290
and I will be by your side forever.

33:01.480 --> 33:03.090
Rongyin's final letter.

33:05.400 --> 33:06.860
It was actually Brother

33:06.890 --> 33:08.670
who returned to the Capital halfway,

33:08.670 --> 33:10.810
causing the fall of Jinzhou.

33:11.960 --> 33:13.860
So Linshan's death

33:15.330 --> 33:18.110
was also caused by him.

33:29.240 --> 33:29.920
Zheng.

33:30.680 --> 33:32.230
The situation is unstable now.

33:31.930 --> 33:34.220
[In Memory of Wan, My Late Mother,
Xie Linshan's Wife]

33:32.680 --> 33:34.790
The soldiers of the Xie Army
are threatening

33:34.220 --> 33:37.220
[In Memory of My Late Father, Xie Linshan]

33:35.000 --> 33:39.000
my brother with their lives to make him
reveal the truth of the Jinzhou case.

33:39.000 --> 33:42.060
I'm caught in the middle,
unable to make my own choices.

33:42.260 --> 33:43.840
Perhaps only my death

33:44.030 --> 33:45.960
can settle this dispute.

33:47.110 --> 33:50.220
I hope this will also awaken my brother's
conscience

33:50.330 --> 33:52.390
and have him give you a chance to live.

33:53.320 --> 33:54.170
Zheng,

33:54.780 --> 33:56.220
do not miss me.

33:57.270 --> 33:59.400
I can't be with you as you grow up.

34:00.110 --> 34:01.250
Mother.

34:01.790 --> 34:03.180
I'm unfilial.

34:04.750 --> 34:06.030
It took me so long

34:06.030 --> 34:08.090
to understand your good intentions.

34:22.460 --> 34:24.920
[Wei Residence]

34:37.250 --> 34:40.570
[Wei Residence]

34:40.110 --> 34:41.370
Stop beating the drum!

34:41.480 --> 34:42.739
Stop beating the drum!

34:44.630 --> 34:46.920
The Princess Royal is here!

34:48.110 --> 34:48.920
Brother!

34:52.920 --> 34:53.590
Your Majesty!

34:53.590 --> 34:54.400
Sister?

34:54.920 --> 34:56.380
I know what you want to say.

34:56.440 --> 34:57.070
But this is not the time

34:57.070 --> 34:58.800
to talk about your friendship with her.

34:58.800 --> 35:00.510
Once the Petition Drum is struck,

35:00.510 --> 35:01.670
the Emperor must hold court

35:01.670 --> 35:03.550
to hear the subjects' pleas or grievances!

35:03.550 --> 35:04.320
Changyu's grievance

35:04.320 --> 35:06.150
has been blown out of proportion
by those with ulterior motives.

35:06.150 --> 35:07.710
The whole world knows about it now.

35:07.710 --> 35:09.640
Brother, you can't hide from this.

35:12.190 --> 35:13.110
Brother!

35:14.550 --> 35:16.100
You framed Xie Zheng

35:17.320 --> 35:18.840
and nearly cost me my life.

35:20.230 --> 35:22.560
I haven't settled this score with you yet.

35:22.880 --> 35:25.600
But if you can show the authority
of an emperor

35:25.710 --> 35:27.480
and clear Changyu's name,

35:28.670 --> 35:30.270
I will wipe the slate clean.

35:35.190 --> 35:35.920
Brother!

35:36.400 --> 35:37.710
One must respect oneself to be respected.

35:37.710 --> 35:39.400
Show the bearing of a true ruler!

35:39.400 --> 35:41.730
Do you want to be a puppet emperor
forever?

35:51.670 --> 35:52.510
Servants!

35:55.150 --> 35:57.150
Summon Fan Changyu for an audience.

35:57.280 --> 35:58.680
Proceed to Chongde Hall.

36:00.360 --> 36:03.220
I am going to exercise
the authority of the Emperor.

36:15.750 --> 36:19.620
[Chongde Hall]

36:17.710 --> 36:20.070
Regarding the unjust case
of Jinzhou 17 years ago,

36:20.070 --> 36:21.590
Wei Qilin was framed.

36:22.760 --> 36:25.000
Today, I, Fan Changyu, stake my life

36:25.710 --> 36:27.040
to implore Your Majesty

36:27.360 --> 36:28.550
to uphold justice

36:30.760 --> 36:32.070
and right the wrongs!

36:41.670 --> 36:42.930
This is the Tiger Tally

36:43.150 --> 36:45.410
Wei Qilin used to seek help in Chongzhou.

36:46.630 --> 36:47.840
This is the truth.

36:48.880 --> 36:50.480
But back then, Lord Changxin

36:50.710 --> 36:52.840
claimed this Tiger Tally was a fake

36:52.960 --> 36:54.480
and refused to send troops.

36:54.480 --> 36:56.810
That is what caused the Jinzhou Massacre.

36:56.840 --> 36:57.670
It shows

36:57.880 --> 37:00.400
that someone
deliberately delayed military action.

37:00.400 --> 37:01.730
The Xie and Wei families

37:02.150 --> 37:03.400
were both framed.

37:08.590 --> 37:10.020
If this is proven true,

37:10.840 --> 37:11.710
Fan,

37:12.480 --> 37:14.880
how do you wish for me
to punish the culprit?

37:15.550 --> 37:16.840
This is a fake.

37:18.630 --> 37:20.280
Shameless.

37:21.360 --> 37:23.290
On what grounds do you call it fake?

37:23.400 --> 37:24.440
On what grounds?

37:25.320 --> 37:27.580
On the grounds that among those present,

37:27.590 --> 37:30.120
the only one
who was there during the massacre

37:30.320 --> 37:31.590
was me.

37:32.590 --> 37:34.320
You claim this is real,

37:35.150 --> 37:36.760
but what proof do you have?

37:37.800 --> 37:40.450
Although I am a new general,

37:40.760 --> 37:41.840
I know that

37:42.590 --> 37:44.520
all Tiger Tallies must be archived

37:44.880 --> 37:46.150
with imprints as proof.

37:46.150 --> 37:47.280
We can compare them.

37:48.710 --> 37:49.800
All paper records

37:49.800 --> 37:52.400
were destroyed in the fire 17 years ago.

37:55.150 --> 37:57.070
How could it be such a coincidence?

37:57.070 --> 37:58.960
It is just that coincidental.

37:59.690 --> 38:01.450
I also know

38:01.550 --> 38:03.710
why you are so obsessed with this.

38:03.760 --> 38:04.890
It's simply because

38:05.070 --> 38:07.880
of your own selfish motives.

38:11.620 --> 38:13.420
[To the Prime Minister]

38:16.440 --> 38:17.580
This is...

38:17.090 --> 38:20.560
[To the Prime Minister]

38:17.800 --> 38:20.730
a handwritten letter from He Jingyuan.

38:21.000 --> 38:25.030
It reveals this girl's true identity.

38:26.380 --> 38:28.490
Your Majesty, please take a look.

38:31.190 --> 38:33.960
Wei Qilin deserted the battle back then

38:33.960 --> 38:35.650
and died a violent death.

38:36.070 --> 38:38.270
The only one who slipped through the net

38:39.400 --> 38:40.790
is you,

38:40.880 --> 38:43.880
Wei Qilin's daughter, Wei Changyu.

38:45.000 --> 38:45.760
Wei Yan!

38:47.400 --> 38:49.320
Stop twisting the facts!

38:49.880 --> 38:51.440
I, Fan Changyu, have a clear conscience!

38:51.440 --> 38:53.090
Wei Changyu

38:53.280 --> 38:55.550
escaped the law back then.

38:55.550 --> 38:58.230
And now she has come to court
to mislead the public

38:58.230 --> 39:00.960
and attempt to destabilize Great Yin.

39:01.000 --> 39:02.710
Her intentions are worthy of execution!

39:02.710 --> 39:03.510
Your Majesty,

39:03.880 --> 39:06.920
today, I am going to impeach
this evil remnant of the Wei family.

39:06.920 --> 39:08.190
She should be sentenced to death

39:08.190 --> 39:09.320
to honor the spirits

39:09.360 --> 39:12.510
of the 100,000 soldiers
who perished at Jinzhou.

39:12.510 --> 39:14.110
Who is the real evil remnant?

39:15.320 --> 39:16.120
Your Majesty!

39:16.280 --> 39:17.480
My Lords!

39:21.110 --> 39:22.960
If my father truly were a villain,

39:22.960 --> 39:25.270
then why would Prime Minister Wei's
trusted aide, General He Jingyuan,

39:23.000 --> 39:29.520
[Diligent and Virtuous]

39:26.030 --> 39:28.030
exchange letters with him

39:28.030 --> 39:30.690
and want to protect the lives
of my sister and me?

39:32.110 --> 39:34.320
I would like to ask Prime Minister Wei
a question.

39:34.320 --> 39:35.600
If my father

39:36.070 --> 39:37.930
were ever to become a big traitor,

39:38.000 --> 39:40.150
who would be the one to benefit
in the end?

39:40.150 --> 39:41.070
Who would?

39:43.080 --> 39:45.320
[Diligent and Virtuous]

39:43.120 --> 39:44.670
General Fan is right.

39:49.760 --> 39:51.090
I would also like to ask,

39:51.550 --> 39:52.920
regarding the case back then,

39:52.920 --> 39:54.630
who benefited the most?

39:59.920 --> 40:01.540
Your Majesty, I heard you intend

40:01.540 --> 40:04.740
to retry the case of the Jinzhou tragedy
from 17 years ago.

40:05.110 --> 40:07.510
This case involves my father, Xie Linshan,

40:07.550 --> 40:08.810
Crown Prince Chengde,

40:08.920 --> 40:10.380
and 100,000 heroic souls.

40:10.440 --> 40:12.550
If the investigation is to be reopened,

40:12.550 --> 40:14.920
how can I be absent?

40:15.680 --> 40:17.280
Neither your national grudge
nor your family grudge

40:17.280 --> 40:18.550
has been avenged yet.

40:19.000 --> 40:19.880
But today,

40:20.880 --> 40:24.480
you're actually asking for rewards
for this traitor's daughter.

40:24.480 --> 40:26.670
The case of the palace burning
has yet to be resolved,

40:26.670 --> 40:28.600
and yet you are here defending her.

40:29.360 --> 40:30.320
Could it be that you,

40:30.320 --> 40:32.510
too, harbor thoughts of rebellion?

40:35.030 --> 40:36.670
I'm afraid the one

40:37.030 --> 40:39.490
with thoughts of rebellion
is someone else.

40:47.710 --> 40:48.510
This letter

40:49.760 --> 40:53.290
is a plea for help written
by Consort Virtue to Wei Yan back then.

40:53.440 --> 40:55.400
Wei Yan, for his own private affection,

40:55.400 --> 40:57.600
returned to the Capital unauthorized,

40:57.840 --> 41:00.480
abandoning the soldiers of Jinzhou
at the front line,

41:00.480 --> 41:01.140
eventually

41:01.400 --> 41:02.860
causing a great disaster.

41:10.300 --> 41:10.750
[Yan, I hope this letter finds you well.
Disaster has struck suddenly.]

41:10.750 --> 41:11.200
[I can only hope you]

41:11.200 --> 41:11.700
[will aid me in this time of peril.]

41:11.700 --> 41:12.200
[The Beijue tribes have invaded
Great Yin, and my father has led the army]

41:12.200 --> 41:12.700
[to resist them. We thought this
would ensure the safety of the country,]

41:12.700 --> 41:13.200
[but it turned out
to be a dark scheme]

41:13.200 --> 41:14.200
[of treacherous men. That foolish ruler
trusted slander too readily.]

41:16.110 --> 41:18.770
It's a case of the guilty
accusing the innocent.

41:18.800 --> 41:19.510
Wei Yan,

41:20.360 --> 41:23.290
you are the biggest traitor
in the Battle of Jinzhou!

41:23.710 --> 41:30.110
[Great Yin Gate]

41:33.210 --> 41:34.590
[Great Yin Gate]

41:37.550 --> 41:42.930
[Yin]

41:40.150 --> 41:42.630
We have our people
within the Imperial Guard.

41:42.630 --> 41:45.160
The palace gates
will fall without an attack.

41:46.190 --> 41:49.800
I have already spread the news
from the Imperial Astronomical Bureau.

41:49.800 --> 41:52.060
The droughts and floods over these years

41:52.550 --> 41:54.710
are all due to a disruption
in the imperial bloodline

41:54.710 --> 41:56.570
and an illegitimate succession.

41:57.440 --> 42:00.440
Your Highness, you're the descendant
of Crown Prince Chengde.

42:00.440 --> 42:03.300
Your succession is the will of the people

42:03.630 --> 42:05.470
and the desire of the officials.

42:06.710 --> 42:07.510
Good.

42:08.280 --> 42:09.970
It has been 17 years.

42:10.400 --> 42:13.320
I have finally returned to this place.
